A ranar Asabar a filin wasa na Stamford Bridge a birnin Landan, a minti na 89, Daniel Sturridge ya zira kwallo a wasan Chelsea, inda ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kaye a gasar Premier.
A lokacin da tawagarsa ke baya da ci 1-0, Sturridge ya samu kwallo daga Sheldon Shakiri, yana da nisan yadi 30 daga Chelsea.
