Guguwar Rosa ta jefa Phoenix, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City cikin barazanar ambaliyar ruwa (yana iya zama mai kyau ga yankunan da fari ya shafa)
Ba kasafai jihar Arizona ke fuskantar matsin lamba ba, amma ragowar ƙarfin guguwar Rosa da ke tafiya a cikin hamadar kudu maso yamma, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa, zai iya zama daidai abin da zai faru a farkon mako mai zuwa.
A halin yanzu, National Weather Service ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar gaggawa don Litinin da Talata ga Nevada da kudu maso gabashin Nevada, Kudancin California da Utah, daga Arizona ta yamma har zuwa Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
