"Babban hadarin da za a iya tsammani daga Guguwar Rosa da sauran ragowar ita ce ruwan sama mai yawa a arewa maso yammacin Baja California da kuma hamadar kudu maso yammacin Amurka", in ji Cibiyar Guguwar Kasa.
