Fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi an "dawo da wani mako" a yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmaya da dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, yayin da Donald Trump ya yi ganawa da mataimakin lauya Rod Rosenstein.
Rosenstein zai kula da ayyukan mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken shigar da Rasha cikin zaben, alaƙar da ke tsakanin magoya bayan Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar shugaba ya toshe shari'a.
