A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya igiya don rikodin tattaunawa da Trump da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarimar 25 ta Tsarin Mulki.
Rosenstein ya musanta rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya je fadar White House a yayin da ake zargin cewa zai yi murabus.
