Aƙalla mutane 384 sun mutu sakamakon girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da tsunami da ya auku a garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ƙaru, in ji hukumomi.
Jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin garin Palu ba, kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 saboda katsewar sadarwa.
A Palau, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Pulau dan Dongan da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke gefen wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka auku, mazauna garin suna bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwar birnin.
Dongola yanki ne da ya kai nisan kilomita 300 (mil 180) a gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Yankin, wanda ke ƙarƙashin yanki, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kamfanonin kamun kifi da noma sune manyan sassan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Dongola.
Harkokin hakar ma'adinai na nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi yana mai da hankali ne a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia, an yi wa Palau da Donggala tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekarar 1996 tsunami ya afku a Donggala ta yamma inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake fuskantar girgizar kasa a cikin tekun Pacific kuma tana fuskantar girgizar kasa akai-akai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh, a gabashin Sumatra, a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh ne.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar tekun yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: An kashe kusan mutane 700 sa'ad da wata guguwa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin tsibirin Java, mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai a bakin teku na Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afku a yankin Pidi Jaya na Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da firgici ta hanyar tunatar da mutane bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na 2004.
Ko da yake ba a yi tsunami ba, amma gine-gine sun rushe kuma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu.
2018: Mutane fiye da 500 sun mutu a girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a tsibirin Lombok, babban tsibirin yawon buɗe ido na ƙasar Indonesia, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido cikin halin rashin taimako na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sara Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin mata
An kama babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, Sarah Palin, a kan zargin cewa ya kai hari kan Palin.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29 daga Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin cin zarafin mata, da shiga cikin rahoton cin zarafin mata, da kuma adawa da kama, a cewar rahoton da mahukuntan jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, ya kwace wayar wata mata da aka sani da rahoton aikata laifuka da aka ce an yi lokacin da ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda.
KTUU ta ruwaito cewa an tsare Palin a harabar Mat-Su Pre-Trial Complex, inda ake tsare da shi a kan takardar shaidar da ba ta da daraja ta $500.
Ya bayyana a kotu ranar Asabar inda aka tambaye shi, inda ya ce "ba shi da laifi", in ji cibiyar.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na wannan rukuni, wanda ke nufin cewa zai iya fuskantar ɗaurin shekara guda da tarar dala 250,000.
An kuma yanke masa hukuncin kisa na aji B wanda zai iya ɗaukar kwana ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tara $ 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da ake tuhumar Palin da aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na shekara ta 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa, Todd Palin hari.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda kuma ta ba da rahoton abin da ake zargi da kai hari.
Yanzu haka an mika karar zuwa kotun Alaska.
An gurfanar da shi a watan Janairun 2016 kan zargin cin zarafin gida, tsoma baki wajen bayar da rahoto kan tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta zarge shi da cewa ya buge kansa a fuskarsa.
A shekarar 2016, kungiyoyin masu ba da agaji sun soki Sarah Palin saboda alakanta halin tashin hankalin ɗanta da yanayin PTSD wanda ya haifar da aikinsa a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Sun Mutu
Aƙalla mutane 384 sun mutu a girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a tsibirin Sulawesi na ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Tsunami da girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta haifar ya lalata dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afku ne a tsakiyar Sulawesi, arewa maso gabashin babban birnin kasar Indonesia, Jakarta.
Bidiyon da ke nuna lokacin da fashewar ta faru yana yawo a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin bakin teku a garin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya faɗi.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi a yankewa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York hukuncin kisa.
Masu gabatar da kara a New York sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga mai laifin harin ta'addanci a birnin New York, Saifullo Saifov, wanda aka yi zargin cewa ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953.
An zargi Sipov, mai shekara 30, da yin amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don murkushe masu tafiya da keke a kan hanyar da ke kan titin Manhattan ta Kudu maso Yamma a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, da'awar da aka shigar a gundumar kudu ta New York, da nufin neman hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su buƙaci tabbatar da cewa Sipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas da kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni.
A cewar takardun kotu, duka biyun suna da hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta gabatar da karar sauraron karar da ta zargi Sipov da laifuffuka 22, gami da aikata kisan kai guda takwas, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma amfani da motoci cikin zalunci da lalata.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi a gaba" kuma masu zargin sun bayyana yadda Saypov ya yi shi a matsayin "ta'addanci, zalunci da cin mutunci".
"Ta hanyar Cifuolo Habbulevik Sipow, Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Anne-Laure Decadette, Darren Drake, Ariel Arledge, Hernan Ferrucci, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnuko sun yi wa iyalai da abokai rauni da lalacewa", in ji sanarwar niyyar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe masu yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kotu a gundumar kudu ta New York.
An yanke wa mai laifin, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shari'ar tarayya a New York, hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe da aka yanke wa ma'aurata ne Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, waɗanda aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa a shekara ta 1953 bayan an tuhume su da yin leƙen asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
A ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, an kashe Rosenberg a kujera ta lantarki.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa abin da ya yi daidai ne.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an sa shi ya kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIL a wayarsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa.
Ya bayyana rashin laifinsa a kan tuhuma 22 da ake masa.
David Patton, wani jami'in tsaro na tarayya da ke wakiltar Sipow, ya ce sun "mamaki" hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Muna tsammanin shawarar da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba zai zama abin mamaki ga duk wanda ke da hannu a wannan lamarin", in ji Patton.
A baya, jami'an tsaron Saipov sun bukaci masu tuhumar da su guji neman hukuncin kisa.
